Package com.ftp.file

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AES
    Class is used for encrypting and decrypting bytes that needs to be sent.
    FolderTreeView
    This class provides tree representation of remote repository folders and files
    FTPFile
    This class is replacement for File class in standard Java library.
    FTPTransferObject
    This is main class used for communicating between server and client.
    KeyGenerator
    This class is used for generating key between server and client using Diffie Hellman algorithm.
    TreeItemSerialisation
    This class contains static methods for serializing and deserializing TreeItem because it is not serializable by default.
    TreeItemSerialisationWrapper<T extends java.io.Serializable>
    This class is wrapper for TreeItem and enables it to be serializable because it is not by default
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FTPCommand
    This enum contains basic FTP commands used to communicate between remote server and client.
